sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Client as Inference Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant REST as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant MM as ModelMesh<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Server as Model Server<br/>8001/TCP gRPC

    %% Flow 1: Model Deployment
    Note over User,Server: Flow 1: Model Deployment
    User->>K8s: POST InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8s-->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8s: Create Deployment<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>etcd: Store Model Metadata<br/>No Auth (internal)
    K8s->>MM: Start Runtime Pod
    MM->>S3: Download Model Artifacts<br/>Auth: S3 Credentials
    S3-->>MM: Model Files
    MM->>Server: Load Model<br/>gRPC/8001
    Server-->>MM: Model Loaded
    MM->>etcd: Update Model Status

    %% Flow 2: Model Inference (REST)
    Note over Client,Server: Flow 2: Model Inference (REST)
    Client->>Router: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>OAuth: Forward Request<br/>HTTPS/8443
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OAuth Token<br/>OpenShift OAuth/6443
    OAuth->>REST: Proxy Request<br/>HTTP/8008 (no encryption)
    REST->>MM: gRPC Inference<br/>gRPC/8033 (no encryption)
    MM->>Server: Model Inference<br/>gRPC/8001
    Server-->>MM: Prediction Result
    MM-->>REST: gRPC Response
    REST-->>OAuth: JSON Response
    OAuth-->>Router: HTTPS Response
    Router-->>Client: JSON Prediction
